      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\u26a0 BRANCH: planning\nat home in Feb. No\ncurrent useful location.\nDenied \u2192 graceful\nempty state. v1 has\nno \"plan-for-elsewhere\"\naffordance (v1.1).",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s343z2r4ultyl",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 995,
      "y": 2295,
      "strokeColor": "#B71C1C",
      "text": "Multi-scenarios:\nFitz I \u00d7 SPF 30 \u00d7 UV 9\n= \"Short\". Fitz I \u00d7\nSPF 50 = still short.\nValidates \"240+ min\"\ncap never kicks in\nfor him. No L3 tap.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
