      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Multi-scenarios:\nFitz I \u00d7 SPF 30 \u00d7 UV 9\n= \"Short\". Fitz I \u00d7\nSPF 50 = still short.\nValidates \"240+ min\"\ncap never kicks in\nfor him. No L3 tap.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true
    },
