      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Picks Fitz IV (her\nactual phototype).\nRE-READS footer:\n\"assumes healthy skin\n+ no photo-sens meds\"\n\u2014 even though she\nalready saw L1.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
