      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\u2605 MOST IMPORTANT L3 TAP IN THE APP \u2605\nVerdict reads \"120 min\" but lived\nexp says ~20 min. TAPS L3 \"Is this\nestimate for me?\" \u2192 AboutView notForMe.\nMentally divides 120 by 4\u20136. Quote:\n\"UV maybe 3 and it looks like I've\nrolled a few. What can I do to stop this?\"",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "id": "mpcde2s3ybeuwqinfp9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1255,
      "y": 2395,
      "strokeColor": "#4A148C",
      "text": "\u2605 L1 re-fires every\ncold launch = HER\nre-attestation surface\nwhen meds change.\nWhy Donatello M1 says\nNO \"Don't Show Again.\"",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T08:27:34.419Z",
