      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\u2605 L1 re-fires every\ncold launch = HER\nre-attestation surface\nwhen meds change.\nWhy Donatello M1 says\nNO \"Don't Show Again.\"",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true
    },
