      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\u26a0 UNDER-PICK RISK\nActually Fitz IV. Self-narrative\n\"I tan, I don't burn\" may push\nhim to Type V/VI. Behavior-first\nrow copy is PARTIAL mitigation \u2014\nhe reads \"rarely burns\" on V and\nself-selects on that clause alone.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true
    },
