      "type": "text",
      "x": 735,
      "y": 2495,
      "strokeColor": "#E65100",
      "text": "Mid-stride tap. Grants.\nButton MUST visibly\nrespond (spinner /\nlocation.fill swap) \u2014\n~2-5 sec fetch feels\nlike eternity in motion.",
