      "type": "text",
      "x": 475,
      "y": 1580,
      "strokeColor": "#5D4037",
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "L1 modal still re-fires every cold launch.\nThe yellow NowView banner is the reach-back\nsurface when the photosensitizer loop is active.\n\nNo special-category-data toggle.\nNo \"Don't Show Again.\"",
      "fontSize": 12,
