      "type": "text",
      "x": 875,
      "y": 1580,
      "strokeColor": "#5D4037",
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "If model output \u2265 240 minutes, the hero number\nDISPLAYS \"240+ min\" rather than the literal\ninteger.\n\nThe cap now lives inside the portrait hero card,\nnot a desktop-style side panel.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T09:11:08.284Z",
