      "type": "text",
      "x": 1275,
      "y": 1580,
      "strokeColor": "#5D4037",
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "Attribution sits in the UV secondary card\nright below the hero and stays visible in the\nsame portrait viewport.\n\n\"Source: Apple WeatherKit\" stays on-screen\nwherever WeatherKit data is shown.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "createdAt": "2026-05-19T09:11:08.285Z",
