      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Inline caveat on the hero card carries the\nlearn-more deep-link into AboutView\n(anchor = `notForMe`).\n\nThis keeps the iPhone layout stacked while\npreserving the L3 reach-back pattern.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
