      "y": 1810,
      "strokeColor": "#5D4037",
      "roughness": 0,
      "text": "When elapsed \u2265 original estimate:\n  \u00b7 Hero card swaps in place to a shield / warn\n    state\n  \u00b7 One warning haptic\n  \u00b7 \"Recalculate\" refreshes UV\n  \u00b7 L2 disclaimer + L3 help stay visible",
